The music, dancing, aesthetic, social, artistic phenomenon described as Acid Jazz dominated for a decade - and has already closed a decade. 
Therefore, is entitled to have its "classics" . 
An original and imaginative blending of different rules and styles of black music, a creative blending jazz, soul, hip hop, funk with dance beats gave new impetus to the music, created new stars and pushed a new generation in the true spirit of jazz: 
the constant and creative change - always with modern conditions and always with knowledge of tradition and history. To remixing of the past with the present in our deck - that is the essence of jazz for all of us. (from liner notes)
